title: Amal Clooney does Print-on-Print Dressing While Pregnant
text: Print-on-Print Maternity Dressing? Amal Clooney Shows How It's Done in Paris February 26, 2017 9:05 PM by Edward Barsamian Photo: Splash News It was only recently that Amal Clooney announced that she’s due with twins, but her maternity style game is already on point. After making a grand red carpet debut at the César Awards in custom Atelier Versace, Clooney took to the streets of Paris in a William Vintage cape dress and a Giambattista Valli floral and fur minidress . And earlier today, Clooney stepped out in her most directional look yet: a mashup of prints that gave ladylike dressing an eye-dazzling spin. Clooney’s tailored topper was the ideal complement to her fluid frock. The moss hue acted as a militaristic spin on the girlish motif, while the black-and-white dress was livened up with chartreuse buds. Over-the-knee boots lent the ensemble with an edgy twist, while an equally graphic tote added feminine flourish. In This Story: Amal Clooney Recommended For You
